{"type": "article", "id": 12448, "title": "Vans Vault Authen 黑色皮款", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-22T07:45:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000225SdwpfVhgL2qE09nz.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t今年黑色皮质单品正火热，从皮裤到皮裙，现在又延伸到了皮制运动鞋。Vans 旗下经典鞋款 Vault Authen 最近推出了全新款式，新款鞋子仍然采用 Vault Authen 经典的设计，而材料采用黑色皮革，搭配非常干净的白色车线，鞋背上是红色的 Logo。运动鞋和皮质，都是当下最热的元素，不知道搭配起来，会不会赢得大家的喜欢。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140212mfEsvt9olOywiq6A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140213zvlTRZB65Y8MWs0Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140213vODRMaCs4SmiFeA3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}